<li><a href="http://www.phy.hk/wiki/englishhtm/TwaveA.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.phy.hk/wiki/englishhtm/TwaveA.htm" rel="nofollow">Simulation of transverse traveling wave</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.acoustics.salford.ac.uk/feschools/" class="external text" title="http://www.acoustics.salford.ac.uk/feschools/" rel="nofollow">Sounds Amazing - AS and A-Level learning resource for sound and waves</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.lightandmatter.com/html_books/3vw/ch03/ch03.html" class="external text" title="http://www.lightandmatter.com/html_books/3vw/ch03/ch03.html" rel="nofollow">Vibrations and Waves - an online textbook</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.physics-lab.net/applets/mechanical-waves" class="external text" title="http://www.physics-lab.net/applets/mechanical-waves" rel="nofollow">Simulation of waves on a string</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cbu.edu/~jvarrian/applets/waves1/lontra_g.htm-simulation" class="external text" title="http://www.cbu.edu/~jvarrian/applets/waves1/lontra_g.htm-simulation" rel="nofollow">of longitudinal and transverse mechanical wave</a></li>
</ul>


